// For a School Operator: //

KSA · Education Investment Intelligence Portal
Sharing a KSA education investment tool I built:
It maps expat population demand by city and curriculum (CBSE, British, IB) against existing school supply — to show where the gaps are.
It also has a live feasibility calculator that builds a full BTL P&L for you.
PLUG IN:

Your Plot Size
No. of Classrooms
Annual Fee per Student
Enrolment Fill Rate

Useful if you're evaluating a KSA site.
